These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, scientist, videographer, engineer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, poppy, lily
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the videographer##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the engineer is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
5. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Job   | security-guard | scientist | engineer | videographer |
| Flower        | iris | daisy   | lily | poppy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
House: wooden, townhouse, cape-cod, tower
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, iris, orchid
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsdaisy is the wooden house##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | cape-cod | wooden  | townhouse  | tower |
| Flower   | orchid    | daisy | iris | zinnia    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, dancing, singing, writing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, almond-milk, fanta
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Hobby          | writing | singing | dancing    | puzzles      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | fanta     | cola | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur, software-developer, paramedic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, coffee, water
1. the entrepreneur is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking water##2
2. the paramedic is on the left of the photographer##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | paramedic | photographer | entrepreneur | software-developer |
| Beverage   | coffee       | iced-tea   | fanta    | water  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
City: berlin, london, nizza, rome
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cricket, skiing, parkour
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| City   | london  | berlin    | nizza   | rome       |
| Sport   | golf | parkour | skiing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, january, july
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, cola
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday   | january      | september | july | march |
| Beverage   | cola | almond-milk     | 7up  | coffee  |

