.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, lily, aconite
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, chinese, dutch
1. the dutch is in an odd position##4
2. the chinese is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the dutch is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the colombian##3
6. the spanish is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite | lily | orchid    |
| Nationality     | dutch | chinese  | colombian     | spanish |

