.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, drama
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, may, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
2. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
6. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person watching crime movies and the person who's birthday is in may##2
8. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | crime      | drama | family |
| Birthday   | august  | february | october    | may            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, coral, pink, aquamarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, superhero, thriller, romance
1. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who likes pink##2
4. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes pink is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | aquamarine | coral   | white | pink |
| Movie-Genre    | romance     | superhero | epic     | thriller  |

