.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, bird, hamster
City: miami, paris, london, colone
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to miami and the owner of the bird##2
4. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Pet      | snake       | bird   | goldfish | hamster |
| City   | london | paris | colone        | miami    |

