.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, marseilles, miami
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, skateboard, taxi
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| City   | san-francisco   | miami   | hannover      | marseilles      |
| Transport      | train | skateboard | taxi | motorbike |

