.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, yellow, lavender, mauve
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, documentary, horror, action
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes lavender is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching horror movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color          | mauve | yellow  | lavender  | ebony |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | horror | spy | documentary   |

