.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, bike, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, golf, cricket, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Transport   | bike | tram | train | trike |
| Sport           | skateboarding     | rugby     | cricket   | golf         |

