.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
City: venice, san-francisco, new-york, liverpool
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, reggae, metal, folk
1. the person traveling to venice is between the fan of country and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| City   | liverpool | san-francisco         | venice   | new-york |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | reggae | folk | country   |

