.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, german, malaysian
House: colonial, tower, palace, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is the german##1
2. the palace house is the thai##1
3. the tower house is the malaysian##1
4. the german is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the thai is in an even position##4
6. the german is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | thai | german    | malaysian |
| House   | colonial   | palace  | ranch-style | tower     |

