.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, brown, red
There 4 different types of food: cherry, lettuce, lemon, nectarine
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
3. the person eating lettuce is the person who likes brown##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
5. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating lemon##2
6. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color         | red   | brown | light-blue | pink    |
| Food   | lemon | lettuce  | nectarine     | cherry |

