.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, tram, boat
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, daffodil, daisy
1. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
7. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter    | tram       | car |
| Flower       | orchid  | daffodil | daisy | zinnia  |

