.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, vegafina, ritmeester, dunhill
There 4 different types of food: apple, garlic, raspberry, cranberry
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | ritmeester | swisher  | dunhill |
| Food     | apple      | raspberry       | garlic | cranberry     |

