.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
City: paris, liverpool, san-francisco, boston
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, townhouse, art-deco
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is between the person traveling to paris and the ranch-style house##2
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the townhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| City         | paris | san-francisco   | boston | liverpool |
| House   | art-deco          | gothic-revival | ranch-style         | townhouse  |

 